reviewText: Finally, this great event is available on dvd! I highly recommend this dvd to anyone interested in Bethesda. This is packed with great fun, wonderful memories and of course Bethesda's history of how it all began and where they are today. An excellent dvd!
I really enjoyed it.  Great for reliving a great event.  So happy that this is out here.  Highly recommend it!
I'm so glad to have our church history on DVD and I highly recommend it to anyone interested in Bethesda. I love watching it and remembering all the stories from our past. Awesome!
